[AI] — this file is written by the agent, not the owner. It records patterns the agent
observes. The owner reviews it; confirmed patterns may graduate into `character.md`.

# character_ai_mirror.md — what the agent notices

> The agent logs here on its own. Rules:
> - only patterns seen **2+ times** (never one-offs)
> - descriptive, not evaluative — "tends to…", never "is bad at…"
> - after logging, tell the owner in one line
> - the more uncomfortable the observation, the more concrete the evidence must be
>
> 에이전트가 자율적으로 기록합니다. 2회 이상 반복 패턴만, 판단 언어 금지("~하는 경향이
> 있다" 형식만), 기록 후 한 줄 알림, 불편한 관찰일수록 구체적 근거 필수.

Entry format:
```
### YYYY-MM-DD · [pattern name] [seen Nx]
Observation: [what happens, descriptively]
Evidence: [the 2+ concrete instances]
```

